Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯獨不想被鮎澤討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 就知道說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直拿我開玩笑 真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 本來還有些感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺也會忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:02:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還沒好好答謝你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 不用謝謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論幾次我都會幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論幾次 我都會讓你喜歡上我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說些…什麼…蠢話…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23小時55分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只剩下5分鐘 但看來還是我贏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護會長的騎士一職
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸你還是退下的好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的被討厭的話 連這種小遊戲都會變得無趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想認真跟我玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 現在才想嚇唬我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長已經睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來的時候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了碓冰的變態白癡台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越來越感覺煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪還有心情睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你整到這地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也懶得管你為什麼討厭女生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你嘗嘗我秘藏的懲罰技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:31.35,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(610,145)}{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\c&HCCF7FD&}{\3c&H2B367B&}{\shad0}{\bord2}校園參觀會上的眼鏡兔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}校園參觀會通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校園參觀會的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向國中三年級生 每年都有辦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決勝負的時刻就要到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將強者納入手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出未來的王牌選手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動社團的盛衰從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是假日舉辦 主要是社團活動介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們都沒關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今年除了社團活動介紹之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還有很多活動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5\pos(180,57)}會長致詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13\pos(260,137)}社團嚮導
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-20\pos(640,107)}星華高校七大不可思議介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七大不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-20\pos(600,183)}治癒點介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食堂人員？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好好玩的樣子 食堂系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.98,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,10)}系？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.98,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,10)}三笨蛋說的才是正確念法 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年舉辦很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參觀路線中 想設一個可愛的食堂來做休息所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那裡佈置成連國中女生也能安心休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適合女生的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備起來應該會很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能夠幫我嗎 我需要人手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟其他女生說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待那些國中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要裝飾些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要想下預算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 應該會有些力氣活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也指望不了其他男生來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的葉爽太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因某些原因 現在是學生會的雜工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是蓋著遮風帽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是一年級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教 葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那總之先去集合人手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從什麼開始著手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從房間裝飾開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉 葉君 雖然不清楚原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要好好幫忙做食堂的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長說以前的事就一筆勾銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,140)\frz-80}抖抖抖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是副會長幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.77,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,260)}食堂負責人 兼 葉監視人 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君 這邊的東西幫忙搬一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 用這個的話 這邊就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用化學室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該不在食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用催眠術…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長到底有幾個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有分裂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人哦 應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 這樣看著葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得哪裡不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是躲著女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是敵視的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又不是女性過敏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那面牆壁不能想想辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 絆到椅子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天小美又休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 小美在不在我們都要來光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才叫真正的愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 確實 碓冰也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊 這是抽獎中的郁金茶和栗子羊羹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 放那邊就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做校園參觀會的準備？很拼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗奈覺得怎樣的學校你才會想進呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准說有抽獎社的高中哦 除此之外都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:37.64,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物徵集社
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了 你就只知道這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.75,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參觀會前一日…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君 再右邊點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點歪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有在努力嘛 葉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲同學 你來看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想服裝就用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很用心準備的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也說很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 這樣…這樣不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 放開手辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.70,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…於是當天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是校內參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 分成好多路線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校內參觀由在校生做嚮導
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人想看到的星華高校肯定不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請選擇自己感興趣的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.84,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高中對社團感興趣的請到這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.37,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化社是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.63,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美術社在這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有治癒點路線呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七大不可思議巡遊路線…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提 不知怎麼選擇路線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想全部體驗的人請到這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問問題也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那第一組出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 麻煩來一個人幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那我們也出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨問隨答路線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天小美果然也是休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天其實不用來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 要我講幾次才明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管小美在不在都要來光顧 才是真正的愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 連碓冰也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼了呢 各位主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們果然只被當可憐人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然今天小美休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是女僕拿鐵的其餘女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將難得地全員出動為各位服務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺飄飄欲仙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄起來了 飄起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特別為各位介紹今天的廚房人員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千和小糯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝平日的惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 第一次出大堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道該說什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好不是神秘生物體在做料理之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 來狂點餐囉 我付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要在客人留言上盡情傾訴我的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 很好 小郁 fight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我寫上噁心的…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是氣勢恢宏的詩詞 滿滿滿滿地寫進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把跟小美充滿回憶的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在腦內來個走馬燈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替您寫上了「很煩」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會造成其他主人的困擾 可以安靜點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用再回來了哦 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 小美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候能聽到她溫柔的話語就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星華高校七大不可思議之二是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理應無人的廣播室裡 突然播放音樂的怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.24,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.61,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動播放設定之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前看來都很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 運動社團就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.60,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用拳套打沙袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先用擒抱來親密接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跟球做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是在做無用功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭呢 這麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很閒的話也不用週末特地來學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣說 我在幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,380)}邪笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當會長的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在比較放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在的話大家都會分心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太顯眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你要這麼說我也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(100,380)}邪笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有份差事一定要你做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有半個人想跟球做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊被擊沉的足球社
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰說他無論如何都想跟球做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我還是第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 碓冰同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請請請 這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來個超帥的射門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球衣也穿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種中學小弟小妹 馬上就能看到超精彩的球技哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球社 碓冰學長在幫忙拉人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也幫我們社團拉人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 為了星華幫運動社炒熱氣氛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍 稍等 我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會接客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:46.51,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實已經準備好葉君的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊們自己玩高興就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那麼淒涼的話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得大家一起努力到現在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好 一起盡興到最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 葉君幫了很多忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一開始經常落跑的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接客我們來 端盤子之類的一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事我們會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 幸村也很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 準備了很適合葉君的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 你們也一起來踢足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和足球做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰同學 接下來是我們棒球社
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他想看的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 在美術室裡接觸到了各種畫材
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在音樂室第一次彈了吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到能如此大開眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 開開心心地參觀到最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乒乓球社 也請你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.38,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來參觀的天才乒乓少女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪條線路最後都是到食堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家走累了 休息之餘順便也來個最後提問時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去跟其他前輩聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請隨便坐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像女僕咖啡店一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們慢慢休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲 哇 你看怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛啊 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲也一起來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來 看上去很順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也有被嚇跑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過搭上話他們就進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面很普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 說實話最初以為會被男生嘲笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到氣氛很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論男女 都會很高興地聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的氣氛變成日常的話 一定會很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同擁有愉快的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是一件很美好的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去看看其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這麼可愛的角色了啊 葉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法啊 被那麼多女的圍著根本沒法逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 難道被扒得光光…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說討厭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼很合適我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可愛的帽子是什麼啊 當我是兔子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人到底什麼眼光啊 女僕裝為什麼能那麼輕飄飄的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼啊 那種生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 果然對女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種生物 肯定會輕易就壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉 你和以前比 現在能看著對方眼睛說話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天應該看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的像你想的那樣 她們柔弱易碎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該面對了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣和女生在一起 還是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(730,180)}亂入的中學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:48.10,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看了高中生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰同學 接下去是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 碓冰同學 幫下我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們社
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先來我們這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.11,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考考看星華吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 想進我們學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太歡迎了 你們喜歡星華啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不過 還是有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我很怕男生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前一直讀的都是女校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是陪我們來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星華男生很多吧 是女校就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你說媽媽崩潰了離家出走是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽太郎 女人比想像中還要纖細脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和女人打交道時也要注意一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(700,340)}父 原摔跤手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.53,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會壞掉的話 我就不接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.27,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 母親只是受夠了父親而離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了 葉君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在收盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不想再接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦接近 也許又會像那時候一樣受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為女人很柔弱 易碎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的像你想的那樣 她們柔弱易碎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕男生啊 就這個有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 眼鏡兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要讓她不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 一點都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該面對了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要施展魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不再對男生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說是魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會用那麼可愛的魔法啊 眼鏡兔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬完這個就可以收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉 幹得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信守約定 之前的事一筆勾銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去時候小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 會長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 辛苦你了 碓冰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備去哪啊 能放下我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不說話啊 喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:20:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了？懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那接下來慰勞下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全都沒來看過我 啊 累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 全托碓冰的福 運動社盛況空前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了 感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能做一些 別人對你做你會高興的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮎澤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能推倒你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:21:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村學長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 真的最尊敬的就是學長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒發覺你是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 葉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想換衣服 制服找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(630,190)}(渚(24)\N 五月的妹妹 \N海之家 beach house 店長)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不停地動來動去 就不會犯睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉要給會長施催眠術的話 催眠點別的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人可以1個月左右不睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那麼我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別當真啊 葉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很唐突 下集講夏天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.82,0:24:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美 女僕拿鐵的大家要一起去海之家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 泳裝都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰 就拜託你當保鏢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.15,0:24:09.77,biaoti2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(750,357)}{\c&H509EF5&}{\fad(300,0)}海之家也是女僕拿鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:06.19,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}どうか Please！can you keep my secret
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:23.20,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(200,200)}キラキラと輝くミラー
